txt.en: While working to secure the Circle of Death in Minas Morgul, you have encountered the Cúrongul - terrible wraiths who serve as the deathless wardens of Barad Cúron.\n\nIf the Rangers of Ithilien intend to maintain a foothold in the Circle of Death, the Cúrongul must be defeated.
You have defeated many of the Cúrongul patrolling the Circle of Death.
At the bidding of Gothmog, the Cúrongul of Minas Morgul serve as wardens of Barad Cúron.
You have banished many of the Cúrongul lurking in the heights of Minas Morgul and made clear the way to Barad Cúron.
Defeat Cúrongul in the Circle of Death ([placeholder]/[placeholder])

Cúrongul can be found throughout the Circle of Death in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou have encountered the Cúrongul, the terrible wardens of Barad Cúron. You should defeat them.
